query:
SELECT 
            t.public_id AS id,
            t.name AS name,
            s.created_at AS solved_at 
        FROM submissions s
        JOIN teams t ON s.team_id = t.id
        JOIN challenges c ON s.challenge_id = c.id
        WHERE c.public_id = $1 
        AND s.is_correct = true
        ORDER BY solved_at ASC
